 feet \\u2013 anyway you like! Unleash your creative side and get ready to rock out.\", \"Dig it\", \"Use the free Skoog App to select your favourite song or playlist in Apple Music or Spotify on your iPad \\u2013 the Skoog App will auto tune your Skoog, so you can create amazing sounds. The built in Lithium-ion rechargeable battery will last up to 10 hours per charge, so you won\\u2019t run out of power mid-session, either.\", \"Thumbs up\", \"Connect to GarageBand and explore even more instruments and sound effects. You can even record your new music and share it with fellow music makers all over the world.\", \"Code away\", \"Skoog brings coding and music to life. In no time at all you\\u2019ll be building your own musical instrument \\u2013 just tap, press or squeeze your Skoog and you\\u2019re off and away.\", \"Access all areas\", \"This app transforms your Skoog into a communication aid. For users with speech or language barriers, this makes communication much easier. Skoog lets you place a picture on each side, so you can communicate with others. You can also navigate your iPhone or iPad using your Skoog or iOS Switch control.\", \"Dimensions\", \"H15 x W13 x D13cm\", \"Weight\", \"585g\", \"Please note: \", \"Skoog is compatible with iPad models that support Bluetooth Low Energy \\u2013 this includes iPad 3rd Generation, iPad 4th Generation, iPad Air, iPad Air 2, iPad mini, iPad mini 2, iPad mini 3 and running iOS 9+.\"]','null','null','null','null','89401710','null','null','585g','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','null','https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/237732560?$rsp-pdp-port-1440$','https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/237732560?$rsp-pdp-port-1440$','https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/237732560alt1?$rsp-pdp-port-1440$','https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/237